.jumbotron.text-center
  %h1 WebSQA
  %p.lead
    A web-based Software Quality Assurance program developed for UMBC's CMSC 345
    course.
.services
  .row
    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.text-center
      %h2 Services Provided
      %hr
  .row
    .col-md-2.col-md-offset-3.text-center
      .service-item
        = fa_icon 'tasks', class: 'service-icon'
        %h4 Progress Tracking
        %p
          Administrators assign tasks and developers report their progress.
          Never miss a deadline again!
    .col-md-2.text-center
      .service-item
        = fa_icon 'bug', class: 'service-icon'
        %h4 Bug Management
        %p
          Report bugs as they arise and be notified when their solutions are
          implemented.
    .col-md-2.text-center
      .service-item
        = fa_icon 'group', class: 'service-icon'
        %h4 Communication
        %p
          WebSQA was designed from the ground up to aid in communication between
          project management and developers.


.signup
  .row
    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.text-center
      %h2 What are you waiting for?
      %hr
  .row
    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.text-center
      %p Click the button below to get started today!
      %p= link_to 'Sign up now', signup_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn btn-primary'
